'''Marcelin Bossou''' (yavutse ku ya 3 Gicurasi 1984) ni umuyobozi wa firime muri [[Togo]], utunganya firime, akaba n'umwanditsi.

== Ubuzima bwa Biografiya ==
Bossou yavukiye i Lomé, muri [[Togo]] mu 1984. <ref name="africine">http://africine.org/personne/marcelin-bossou/31294</ref> Yari umuhungu w'ababyeyi bo muri Bénin. <ref>https://www.style-evidence.com/pages/showcases/marcellin-bossou/</ref> Se wa Bossou yari umuyobozi w'ikigo cy'imikino. . Yakoraga kuri tereviziyo yigenga ya Radio Télévision Delta Santé nk'umutekinisiye nyuma aba umuyobozi. <ref name="courrier">https://blog.courrierinternational.com/l-afrique-en-films/2014/03/14/cineafriqua86-marcelin-bossou-parle-du-cinema-togolais/</ref>

Muri 2008, yiyandikishije muri Ecole Supérieure des Arts Visuels  i Marrakesh muri [[Maroc]] nyuma yo kubona buruse. Bossou yayoboye filime ye ya mbere ngufi, ''La Bourse ou la vie'' na ''L'inconnu'' mu 2010. <ref name="courrier" /> Yabonye uruhushya rwe muri Film Studies, Directory option, muri 2012. Filime ya Bossou yahawe impamyabumenyi, ''Nuit de Noces'', yinjiye mu birori byinshi bya firime nka Mediterranean Short Film Festival ya Tangier, Iserukiramuco rya Filime nyafurika rya Luxor, hamwe na Festival ya Afrika ya Poitiers. ''Nuit de Noces'' yakiriye Grand Prix mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Atakpamé i Togo ndetse nigihembo cyihariye cya René Monory mu Iserukiramuco rya Filime na Televiziyo bya Panafrican ya Ouagadougou .  Irasuzuma imitwaro abagore bahura nazo iyo bashyingiranywe, harimo no kwerekana ubusugi bwabo. <ref>https://www.africardv.com/societe/togo-marcellin-bossou-et-les-jeunes-de-lai-parlent-de-droits-sexuels/</ref>

Nyuma yo guhabwa impamyabumenyi, Bossou yayoboye ''L'anniversaire'' .  Yashinze isosiyete ikora amajwi n'amashusho Marbos Productions i Lomé muri 2015. Intego nyamukuru yaryo ni ugutanga inkunga kubanyeshuri biga muri firime ya Togoliya kugirango bakore film zabo za mbere. <ref>http://africultures.com/structures/?no=13345</ref> Muri 2015, yayoboye ''Les deux frères'' . Filime yahawe igihembo cyo gufotora neza mu iserukiramuco rya Clap Ivoire.  Muri 2019, Bossou yakoze firime ''La vie de Daniel'' iyobowe na Gilbert Bararmna na ''Femme'' Ebène na Rachel Kpizing. <ref>https://www.africardv.com/culture/deux-films-togolais-recompenses-au-benin/</ref>

Kuri ubu Bossou arimo akora kuri firime ye ya mbere yerekana, ''Broken Drums'', biteganijwe ko izasohoka mu 2021. <ref>http://www.scenarioaulongcourt.com/Marcelin-BOSSOU</ref> Yigisha isesengura rya firime, kwandika na tekinike mu Ishuri Rikuru rya Sinema  i Lomé. 

